Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:05.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,およそ遠しとされしもの　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:08.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,下等で奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:13.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見慣れた動植物とは　まるで違うと　おぼしきモノ達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それら異形の一群を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:20.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヒトは古くから畏れを含み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつしか総じて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:25.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「蟲」と呼んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:11.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父は酔うと　よくこんな話をした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:15.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何年前になるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:21.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ある晩　隣の村から帰る途中で道に迷ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:28.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,散々歩き回るも　とうとう道すらなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:30.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,困り果てていると
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:37.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人だ　助かった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あっちに道が…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　あの灯りは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:02.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,近づくと　得も言われぬ酒の馨しい匂いが漂ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:08.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そのうち一口　その酒を飲んでみたくなり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっそりと宴の中に紛れ込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:21.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その酒は黄金色の光を帯びていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:42.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,禄助　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:43.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ご苦労だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前も今日は　家に戻ってのんびりするといい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:52.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの　蔵元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:01.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今年の酒　少しばかり持って帰りたいのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　いいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:09.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今年のできなら　親父さんもお前の酒を認めてくれるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,子どもの頃　よくこうして　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:29.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父の作った酒を　隣の村まで届けに行ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:36.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんな時　山道に入ると
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:39.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつも何かに纏わり付かれるような気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あぶねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:55.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして　やっとの思いで使い先へ着いた頃には
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,明らかに酒の量が減ってしまっているのだった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:07.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの時　それを蔵元に告げられ　私はひどく叱られたが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:11.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父は　それを咎めようとはしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:17.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　山で何かに絡まれたか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだか目に見えないものがずっと周りにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:26.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それで　気が付いたら酒が減ってて　本当だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:33.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか　あれらは　旨い酒が好物なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:37.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうやら　今年の酒も気に入ってくれたようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　まだまだだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの酒に比べれば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前にも話したことがあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「光る酒」だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの味が今でも忘れられんでな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:02.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんはずっとあれを目指してるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,酒は生き物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:11.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,感覚を全部使って　言葉のすべてを聞き取れれば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いずれはきっと答えてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,言葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:23.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　お前も跡を継ぐ気なら　それをよーく覚えておきな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ついにできたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:48.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,旨い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだか足が縺れるな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:06.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,酔っちまったか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:12.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　ここ　どこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どっかで道を間違えたか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:17.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,戻るか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だこりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,けものの毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっ　おい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,待て　こら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこ行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このっ　返せっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　あの灯り
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな所で　一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:05.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何してんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　その…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　光酒持ってんじゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　遠慮することはねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光る酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:38.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それじゃ　これは　父さんの言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見ねえ顔だな　新参蟲師か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,酒をやれば　離れるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蟲師…この人らが…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よぉ　ギンコ　蟲煙草のいいのがあるぞ　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,へえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒と交換でどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:37.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ　切らしちまったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺ももうほとんど残っていねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,頼む　一滴でいいからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ　そのタバコ全部となら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:50.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒切らしたあんたが悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　そう言うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう　あんただよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:04.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そん中　光酒だろう　ちょっとばかし分けてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,随分重そうじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:10.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ケチケチすんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,タバコがいらねんなら　他にもいろいろあるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この盃　どこかで…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでも名のある器だそうでな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:29.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔　光酒一杯と交換してやったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　兄ちゃんお目が高い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:36.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その後　売りに行ったら　ガラクタ同然と言われたわけだが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,てーめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:41.04,TXT JP (O-UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　ギンコ　余計なこと言うんじゃねえよ　このっ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:41.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんだ　これは父さんがいつも持ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:44.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　人の商売邪魔していいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これをもらえるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒とそれ　変えてくれんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　まあ　構わねえが…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ありがとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:56.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:58.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,飲まないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:04.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういえば　誰もあの光る酒を飲んではいない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体　あの酒は何のために…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかし　遅いな　ワタリの連中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何やら　準備に手間取っているようだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,準備？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,またか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちっと様子見てくるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺も…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:28.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,兄ちゃん　光酒　たんまり持ってんね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺にも分けてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わしもわしも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:33.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ええ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:46.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰だい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イサザ　俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:50.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ギンコか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,達者にしてたか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:54.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おかげさんで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:57.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じき始めるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今　場所が定まったところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:04.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光脈のへそが　また見つけにくくなってんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:10.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　ここも古い光脈だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:15.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,次からは　別の光脈から分けてもらったほうがよさそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:18.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,寿命か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,地中深くにもぐるだけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっとまた　力を蓄えたら戻ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:43.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何が始まるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光る酒が増えた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体どういうからくりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　おかしいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしや　偽物か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:12.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ち…違う　俺じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あっ　あいつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつから買ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,偽物持ち込んだのはあいつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　待って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,捕まえろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:31.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺なんか　まずいことしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,速く山を降りよう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:50.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　こっち
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:50.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,待ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:53.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,悪気はなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:58.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺はただ　あんたらの光る酒を飲んでみたくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,同業のふりして紛れ込んだのは謝る
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:03.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,けど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　虫師じゃねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:10.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　俺は麓の郷の蔵人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:12.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蔵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:14.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ　その酒は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今年　うちのくらで造った酒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:23.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何年も　試行錯誤して　ようやくできた酒なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,病で臥せってる父に飲ませてやりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:29.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,持って帰る途中　道に迷って
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,紛れ込んちまっただけなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうか見逃してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体　どうやって造った
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,杜氏だった父が倒れてから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:46.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うちのくらの酒はすっかり味が落ちてしまってな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父のいう通りに　やってるつもりだったが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:54.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうすぐに　父の経験に追いつけるはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:58.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それでも　くらの名を落としたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,米を変え　水を変え
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,手を尽くしたが無駄だった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:09.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だがある時　ふと　酵母を換えるとどうなるかと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:15.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うちではずっとくらにいる酵母を使ってきたが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:18.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,野生のもので試してみようと思ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,酵母は糖分を好むため
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,花の蜜にいる酵母を集めて歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:28.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それらを増やして使ったが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほとんどは大した変化は見られなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:36.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　たっだ一つの樽だけが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,黄金色に輝く　美酒となった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,花の蜜から？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その酒　飲んでも異常なかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,少量じゃわからなかったんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:56.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと妙な酔い方をしたな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,赤黒い毛の幻覚を見えたり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃ幻覚じゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:03.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,猩々の髭って虫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,虫師が講を行う時の案内に使う
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:11.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,酒を好む虫は多いが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やつらは光酒だけを巣に持って帰る
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:17.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やつらまで騙されたわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:18.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大したもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいだろう　あんたの話　信じよう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見逃してくれるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その代わり　その酒を世に出すのはやめてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,酔うと虫が見える酒なんざ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,出回ったらいろいろ無駄な騒ぎになりだね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それにいくら味がよくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:45.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,幻が見えるんじゃ　あんたらにとってもいい評判にはならない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:54.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おそらく　あんたが酵母の代わりに使ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,吸蜜糖って虫だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:02.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,酵母と同様　糖を食って酒とする微細な虫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒偽造の原料として用いるという説はあると
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,成功した例はいまだ聞かない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたの蔵人としての技量は確かってことだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,聞いていいか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:22.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの光酒　とは一体　なんなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,生命そのものの姿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,虫わずらいには万薬の長だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:31.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,虫とは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　世を構成してるものの一部さね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:42.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それ以上でも　以下でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ところで　あんたの造った酒な
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,世に出せないってのは表向きにって話ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:03.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,翌朝　くらへ引き返すと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:08.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,酒に酔った蔵人たちや蔵本が幻覚を見たと騒ぎになっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:15.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,話し合った結果　その酒の出荷は取りやめとなり
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:18.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,当面　奥のくらにおいておくことにした
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:23.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,というのも　時折妙な客が訪れ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その酒を買っていくようになったためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:31.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの人ら　一体どこであの酒の話　聞きつけてきてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:33.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,表向きにはって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺らにとっちゃ使える酒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,噂流しといてやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おもしろい酒造るくらがあるってな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなことしたらあいつら　捕まえにくんじゃないか　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ただ売るだけなら問題ねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:57.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さっきは光酒として取引したのはまずかったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,要は　使え用だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どう使うんだ
